Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Comment: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁天丸虽然平安无事出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是海贼营业却相当辣手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心谨慎加上琐碎的步骤…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于往往只看重结果的帆船部部员来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们能够完成这项工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 猛烈宇宙海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次工作！白凰海贼团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:23:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(endcard)
